{
  "stem": "10699.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Therefore, a girl that was sleeping like a sardine and with her legs on my tummy scratched me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that scratch became an anthrax [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] because, there-- you know, there were dirty feet and dirty nails.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to this day, I feel it, because eventually, they put in-- they didn't have much, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It became an anthrax.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she had nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So without anesthetic or anything, she, she pierced it, put some kind of gauze in it with a disinfectant, right?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but there was nobody to look after it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because after that-- that was-- must have been quite a time later, because when they took it out, there was now maggots in it, full of maggots, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just maggots that had grown in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that left me with a scar that I can even today tell the change of weather.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the conditions in Bergen-Belsen were just that you were here to die, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in barracks, except for being-- go for Appell, being beaten up for no reason whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Food I cannot remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on one Appell on the 1st of January-- because I will never forget it because I knew it was the 1st of January-- they made a general Appell-- 'Appell,' it means 'call-up' in Bergen-Belsen-- where everybody had to come out in the open and stand.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The sick, the old, the-- everybody had to come out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had to stand there 12 hours in the snow and ice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they just wanted to watch how many will die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And a few of us came out of that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So that was the 1st of January, '45, yeah?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
